| jade vs sapphire | 22.1 | Clearly distinct |
| rose-dim vs ghost | 12.7 | Distinct (though both muted) |
| amber vs rose-bright | 24.6 | Very distinct |
| violet vs sapphire | 15.3 | Distinct |

